*Murray, C.A. and Grier, D.G., ''Colloidal Crystals'', Amer. Scientist, Vol. 83, p.&amp;nbsp;238 (1995);
*''Video Microscopy of Monodisperse Colloidal Systems'', Ann. Rev. Phys. Chem., Vol. 47, p.&amp;nbsp;421 (1996)
*Tanaka, 1992, Phase Transition of Gel
{{Div col end}}

